#

Spicy Chickpea Tacos

30 min
$12
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-free

Cuisine:

MexicanAmerican

Course:

MainLunch

Tags:

quickeasytacosspicyhealthy

Description

Quick and flavorful tacos packed with spicy chickpeas, fresh veggies, and zesty lime!

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • chili powder: 1 tsp
  • cumin: 1 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • corn tortillas: 8 small
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, cut into wedges
  • red onion: 1/2, diced
  • sour cream or greek yogurt: 1/2 cup (optional)
